title: Gentlemen 1.0 (LF Official - CRACKTRO)
description:
Gentlemen! is a frantically paced two player Victorian-themed duelling game.

Go head-to-head with your frenemy in 19th Century England, settling your grievances with knives, bombs, deadly homing pigeons, and more.

You'll need to hone a delicate balance of technique, knowledge, cunning, and blind panic (just like a real duel). You'll also need a friend - two players, one screen. If you don't have a friend, go and get one. 

includes cracktro bonus (pirate exclusive shiz).
